{"tid":1342160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來係00:16出政府新聞稿！！","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:33:48.000Z","uid":37577,"like":1,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc1c03f5b606b6df06a43294647ccdcc6179fa1","tid":1342160,"uid":37577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"政府強烈譴責暴力行為<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　就昨日（七月二十一日）晚上在上環及元朗發生的暴力行為，特區政府作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n　　繼之前衝擊中聯辦大樓後，再有激進示威者無視警方多次警告，在上環一帶向警方發動連番暴力襲擊，包括投擲汽油彈、縱火、擲磚，亦堵塞主要幹道，行為令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n　　與此同時，在元朗有人聚眾在港鐵車站月台及車廂內襲擊乘客，引發衝突，導致有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n　　香港作為法治社會完全不能容忍任何暴力行為，特區政府予以強烈譴責，並會嚴正追究。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月22日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間0時16分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/22/P2019072200010.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F22%2FP2019072200010.htm&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1GAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=f04849f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/22/P2019072200010.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6fd1ea0328f961599d8e7c23df89dc987d1fa5d9","tid":1342160,"uid":87921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:18:54.000Z","msg":"投擲汽油彈？"},{"pid":"43161d58db68a0e82f3f877614d7add2b7f32b2e","tid":1342160,"uid":3765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:19:08.000Z","msg":"好撚野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入晒黑衫人到"},{"pid":"8b962f41ba638386e038604df44a25722bdb701a","tid":1342160,"uid":45040,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:19:30.000Z","msg":"元朗嗰啲叫衝突,我屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae1af20bc043d91a9ad823dfd08453a50ce31ae","tid":1342160,"uid":37577,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"係威既 將兩件事拉埋一齊講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"